io.r2dbc.proxy.listener

Interface LifeCycleListener

  • Deprecated. 
    Use ProxyMethodExecutionListener

    @Deprecated
public interface LifeCycleListener
    Provides callback methods for each SPI call.
    Author:
    Tadaya Tsuyukubo
    See Also:
    LifeCycleExecutionListener

      • beforeMethod

        default void beforeMethod(MethodExecutionInfo methodExecutionInfo)
        Deprecated. 
        Called at every method invocation. When any methods on proxied classes are called, this callback is called first. Then, corresponding beforeXxxOnYyy callback will be called. Analogous to ProxyExecutionListener.beforeMethod(MethodExecutionInfo)
        Parameters:
        methodExecutionInfo - method execution info

      • afterMethod

        default void afterMethod(MethodExecutionInfo methodExecutionInfo)
        Deprecated. 
        Called at every method invocation. When any methods on proxied classes are called and after actual method is invoked, corresponding afterXxxOnYyy callback is called, then this callback method will be invoked. Analogous to ProxyExecutionListener.afterMethod(MethodExecutionInfo)
        Parameters:
        methodExecutionInfo - method execution info

      • beforeQuery

        default void beforeQuery(QueryExecutionInfo queryExecutionInfo)
        Deprecated. 
        Called before execution of query. When query is executed, this callback method is called first, then beforeExecuteOnStatement(QueryExecutionInfo) or beforeExecuteOnBatch(QueryExecutionInfo) will be called. Analogous to ProxyExecutionListener.beforeQuery(QueryExecutionInfo)
        Parameters:
        queryExecutionInfo - query execution info

      • afterQuery

        default void afterQuery(QueryExecutionInfo queryExecutionInfo)
        Deprecated. 
        Called after execution of query. When query is executed, after original method is called, then afterExecuteOnStatement(QueryExecutionInfo) or afterExecuteOnBatch(QueryExecutionInfo), then this method is invoked. Analogous to ProxyExecutionListener.afterQuery(QueryExecutionInfo)
        Parameters:
        queryExecutionInfo - query execution info
